window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>I Am Shaolin</i> is the story of an infant child saved from a perilous ending by fate. She was raised in such a unique setting for safety and given the name Shaolin Starr, The \"Gentle Warrior\", and how she became such.</p> <p>Because of the failed kidnapping attempt on her life as an infant child, Shaolin never knows what it was like to experience the normal life as a girl child growing up. No, she was born having emerald green eyes. Nevertheless, as fate has it, she learns the way of the Shaolin Temple.</p>"; 
